say for the record that we are meeting today on short notice on the 
nominations  of  Mario  Cino  and  Phyllis  Scheinberg.  The  President 
nominated Mario Cino to be Deputy Secretary of Transportation on 
April  6th  and  Ms.  Scheinberg  was  nominated  on  April  14th.  Each 
has  come  to  us  with  tremendous  recommendations  and  there  has 
been an expression of urgency that we proceed with these nomina-
tions. 

