Senator  LAUTENBERG.  Well,  I  can  see  that  Secretary  Mineta  has 
had  a  chance  to  impart  his  wisdom  and  knowledge  to  each  of  you. 
The  words  are  not  really  comforting,  though  they  are  nicely  said 
